metadata.title: 2063artists(various) - jardin numerique - wireless digital music [63_050]
metadata.description: We have two reason to be in gala mode: Five years of 2063 and 050 releases counting on 2063 (not counting the LPs). This made me organize a little 'shopwindow' on the 'lange nacht der kultur' in the very homebase of 2063music, Octagone and Tonatom: Kaiserslautern. Tonight I will play a ambientmix with special visuals to bring our great music to the peoples. For the ones who cannot join this event I compiled this little compilation for your convenience. Big, big, big thanks go to all the artists and other people who support this label and the spirit of netaudio. For additional infos on the tracks visit 2063music website! 2063music.de
